main event: An observer spotted a phenomenon in the sky while traveling on Highway 60 in Ontario, California, during the evening.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 15-20 minutes,The observer described the phenomenon as pulsating and bright, similar to a star or planet,The observer noted that an aircraft was seen maneuvering around the object during the sighting,This was the 22nd UFO the observer reported sighting,The report concluded that it was an unreliable sighting.
sighted object: a bright, pulsating object in the sky
witness description: Gary T. Varner, a 17-year-old male, who reported the sighting and has seen a total of 22 unidentified objects.
